# Privacy Policy / Gizlilik Politikası

**Akciğer Sağlık** · Android paket adı: `com.bbabur.akcigersaglik`

Last Updated / Son Güncelleme: 2026-04-12

---

## English

### Information we process
Health-related inputs you provide (for example age, smoking habits, exercise, breath quality) are **processed on your device**. Summary scores and related app state may be **stored on your device** (local storage) so they can persist between sessions. **We do not operate a backend that receives your health questionnaire answers from the app.**

The optional **“I quit smoking”** section stores your quit date, badges, certificates, pledge text, and related preferences **only on your device**. This data is **not transmitted** to our servers by the app (we do not collect it centrally).

### Advertising
The app may show **Google AdMob** ads (for example banner and interstitial formats). Google may process data according to Google’s policies. See: [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy).

### Third-party services (examples)
- **Google (AdMob):** ad delivery and measurement as described by Google.
- **Expo / EAS (if enabled):** the published build may use Expo tooling for over-the-air updates; update manifests are served by Expo’s infrastructure. Health inputs you type in the app are not sent to us as a form submission through this policy’s “app author” channel.

### Data retention
Data stored locally remains until you uninstall the app or clear app data / storage from device settings, unless the app provides an in-app reset.

### Health disclaimer
The app is **informational / wellness-oriented** and is **not** a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.

### Children’s privacy
The app is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

### Changes
We may update this policy; the date at the top will change.

### Contact
Questions: burakbabursah@gmail.com

